# Phase 1: Analyze the Fix

This is a patch for InstCombine, ValueTracking:

InstCombine: Handle fdiv in SimplifyDemandedFPClass

diff --git a/llvm/include/llvm/Support/KnownFPClass.h b/llvm/include/llvm/Support/KnownFPClass.h
